  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Creates a color ramp (gradient) that gradually transitions between colors specified in the colors input list.</p><p>The lists Colors and Positions must have the same number of elements. Together, they define the list of control points used for the spline interpolation.</p><p>Note: From now on, PxrRamp will internaly add extra points to the spline to output the expected result. Previously, the ramp needed at least 4 points and required extra knowledge from the user. This is no longer necessary.</p><h3 id=\"PxrRamp-InputParameters\">Input Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-RampType\">Ramp Type</h4><p>Controls the direction in which the ramp colors change.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"201d72f6-ffbb-4d6f-b0c0-0586ff65e2db\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRampType0.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampType0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224500\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampType0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0b4f670d-a911-487d-b991-9e0f2127476e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRampType1.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampType1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224497\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampType1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0ba7c82b-e31b-466a-a5e0-1884f2ea88f2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616223&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRampType2.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampType2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224494\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampType2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9ed00e8a-5c91-48b2-ae18-49e8498c1bba\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRampType3.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType3.png?version=1