\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampType4.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cb3f1fc6-cfb8-4e97-bc69-c5d1b1fc1972\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType4.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616025&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRampType5.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampType5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224485\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampType5.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6209b716-f691-4900-bd2c-0984ea49fc1c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRampType6.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampType6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224482\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampType6.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a24bdbb5-3e85-4b83-b2ee-495f1178103b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType6.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=256 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"pxrRampType7.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=125&amp;height=125\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampType7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"125\" data-width=\"125\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224479\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampType7.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7ec8d276-3272-490f-a72f-6ec73ca7f7fb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=125&amp;height=125 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampType7.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615839&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=125&amp;height=125 1x\"></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-Tile\">Tile</h4><p>Determines whether the ramp texture is repeated.</p><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-Reverse\">Reverse</h4><p>If enabled, this flips the ramp so it reverses direction.</p><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-SplineType\">Spline Type</h4><p>Controls the way the intermediate colors between the colors listed in the colors list are calculated. Or you may choose &quot;constant&quot; (&quot;None&quot; in 21 ) for no blending between the selected colors.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrRamp_spline_linear.png\" width=\"258\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_linear.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=258&amp;height=112\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_linear.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"91\" data-width=\"209\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224473\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrRamp_spline_linear.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"99328449-748e-410e-a3ca-b53d7cfcdd61\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_linear.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=418&amp;height=182 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_linear.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=258&amp;height=112 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrRamp_spline_constant.png\" width=\"258\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_constant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=258&amp;height=112\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_constant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"91\" data-width=\"209\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224470\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrRamp_spline_constant.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a180c679-d9e4-482d-a289-0f444c54551b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_constant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=418&amp;height=182 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_constant.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=258&amp;height=112 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrRamp_spline_catmullrom.png\" width=\"256\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_catmullrom.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=111\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_catmullrom.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"91\" data-width=\"209\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224476\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrRamp_spline_catmullrom.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5bd4cb22-f092-4134-8b44-51782869a0d3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_catmullrom.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=418&amp;height=182 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/PxrRamp_spline_catmullrom.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330615614&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=256&amp;height=111 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h4 id=\"PxrRamp-SplineMap\">Spline Map</h4><p>If connected to a pattern, this is the 1D manifold that controls the map of the ramp. For example, if you connect this to a noise pattern, then the direction of the changing colors in the ramp will follow the noise pattern. This map takes precedence over the manifold value if both are connected.</p><p>The following image shows a PxrVoronoise pattern (with frequency set to 10) connected to a ramp through the splineMap parameter. The black values from the noise pattern are mapped to red from the ramp, and the white values from the noise are mapped to blue from the ramp, and the values between that are mapped to the green color from the middle of the ramp.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampSplineMap.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampSplineMap.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"256\" data-width=\"256\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224527\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampSplineMap.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1d2b731f-d29d-40bb-ab10-eff0770f0cd1\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-RandomSource\">Random Source</h4><p>When Ramp Type is set to &quot;Random Object Color&quot;, PxrRamp will use either the object's ID (Attribute &quot;identifier:id&quot;) or the object's name (Attribute &quot;identifier:name&quot;) to compute a random seed. This seed will be used to pick a color in the ramp.</p><p>This example uses the &quot;None&quot; Spline Type, but other spline types are supported.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"400\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"200\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224524\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampRandomObjNone_render.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"57f63f6d-a7a9-480b-9ca1-8f2dcd9b2aef\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=200 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_render.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=200 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"350\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_ramp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=87\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_ramp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"87\" data-width=\"350\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224521\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrRampRandomObjNone_ramp.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cd0872c0-5abf-4474-adc2-f7f641737db1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_ramp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=87 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrRampRandomObjNone_ramp.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616580&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=350&amp;height=87 1x\"></span><p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"454\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrVaryPinwheelSM.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224458/pxrVaryPinwheelSM.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224530\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"pxrVaryPinwheelSM.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224458\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"dd982c6b-e810-418b-a653-cdcb56e20522\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrVaryPinwheelSM.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542224458/pxrVaryPinwheelSM.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330616751&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-RandomSeed\">Random Seed</h4><p>Change this value to get a different set of random variations.</p><p /><h3 id=\"PxrRamp-ColorRamp(Manual)\">Color Ramp (Manual)</h3><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-Manifold\">Manifold</h4><p>Controls the 2D placement of the ramp. Defaults to using the s and t values of the surface geometry to place the ramp colors on the surface.</p><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-MatchC++patterns\">Match C++ patterns</h4><p>Match RenderMan23 C++ scenes but may slow down your render.  Use only when necessary.</p><h3 id=\"PxrRamp-OutputParameters\">Output Parameters</h3><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-resultRGB\">resultRGB</h4><p>The clamped color result.</p><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-resultR\">resultR</h4><p>The R channel from the resultRGB output.</p><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-resultG\">resultG</h4><p>The G channel from the resultRGB output.</p><h4 id=\"PxrRamp-resultB\">resultB</h4><p>The B channel from the resultRGB output.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
  },
